  <h2>Customer success stories</h2>
  <ol>
    <li class="note"><b>Birthday fix</b>: last-minute dessert flight, mariachis did <i>Las Mañanitas</i>. Family happy, photos for days.</li>
    <li class="note"><b>Study group fuel</b>: Friday food truck drop at Memorial Mall kept a 6-person cram alive. <i>No one crashed.</i></li>
    <li class="note"><b>Date night rescue</b>: table by the band, split fajitas, free churros after 9. <u>They booked again next week.</u></li>
  </ol>

